# Backend Architecture (V2.1)

**Authority:** `00_architecture_authority.mdc` · **Detail:** `doc/ARCHITECTURE_V2_AGENT_RULES.md` §8

## Layer pattern

```
modules/<domain>/routes/       ← HTTP, Zod validation, sendSuccess/handleRouteError
modules/<domain>/services/     ← business logic, rowTo*Api()
modules/<domain>/repositories/ ← TenantRepository subclasses
```

Legacy `backend/src/routes/*.ts` are **@deprecated re-exports only**. Register new routers in `mountVersionedApi.ts`.

